    dc:creator "He, Zhixin; Ma, Ge; Long, Jifeng; Wang, Yan; Zhang, Tao; Ma, Libin" ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomy of scaly crickets (Orthoptera: Mogoplistidae: Mogoplistinae) from China: five new species groups and three new species of the genus Ornebius Guérin-Méneville, 1844" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596137>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596157>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596165>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596169> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596137>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Genitalia of three individuals of O. aurumalas He, Zhang & Ma, sp. n. in lateral view. According to the figures, it is difficult to judge species from the lateral view of genitalia, because there are intra-specific differences between individuals of O. aurumalas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4596137/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596157>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Sclerotized parts of male genitalia of O. rubidus. Line drawing from Ingrisch (2006). lv= lateral valve of central phallic lobe; is= internal sclerite of lateral valve." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4596157/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596165>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Male phallic complex all after cleaning in protease solution. Sclerotized parts of male genitalia of O. carnificare (F), O. samudra (A), O. tuberculatus (B), O. aureus (C), O. peniculatus (D) and O. cibodas (E) in lateral views. Line drawings (A–E) from Ingrisch (2006). es= external sclerite of lateral valve; mv= medial valve of central phallic lobe, ss= spermatophore sac." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4596165/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596169>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Sclerotized parts of male genitalia of O. pullus. Line drawing from Ingrisch (2006). ed= ejaculatory duct; lv= lateral valve of central phallic lobe; mv= medial valve of central phallic lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4596169/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

